text: Barney (Stallone), Christmas (Statham) and the rest of the team comes face-to-face with Conrad Stonebanks (Gibson), who years ago co-founded The Expendables with Barney. Stonebanks subsequently became a ruthless arms trader and someone who Barney was forced to kill... or so he thought. Stonebanks, who eluded death once before, now is making it his mission to end The Expendables -- but Barney has other plans. Barney decides that he has to fight old blood with new blood, and brings in a new era of Expendables team members, recruiting individuals who are younger, faster and more tech-savvy. The latest mission becomes a clash of classic old-school style versus high-tech expertise in the Expendables' most personal battle yet.

text: Les critiques nous avaient déjà fait le coup avec Expendables 2!!! et les revoilà qui récidivent! Les critiques ont l'air d'être de ceux qui ont loupé l'école du cinéma... Il en faut pour tout les goûts, Expendables 3 est bien dans la continuité du 1 et du 2. Ceux qui veulent des films scénarios extraordinaire et des dialogues de bourgeois n'ont qu'à passer leur chemin et ne pas dégoûter les autres. Par contre si vous cherchez un film d'action pour vous changer les idées, vous divertir... foncez tête baissé. Cet Expendables 3, remplit parfaitement le cahier des charges qu'on lui demande: de l'Action, un brin d'Humour bien dosé et ce mélange des générations qui fonctionne bien. Si vous lisez ceci et que vous êtes septique (comme la fosse) allez le voir et faites-vous votre propre opinion, c'est ce que j'ai fait! et je ne suis pas déçu du voyage.

text: Here's how I would've done the movie as a writer. Barney is blinded by revenge after Cesar nearly dies, so the expendables want to handle it without him by having him take a little vacation. Meanwhile smilee is actually Barney's son whose hunting his "uncle" Conrad for the CIA. He won't kill him because of his love for Stonebanks and its why his team was ambushed and captured before he is taken in for the war crimes. So Barney has to put aside his rage and prove to the expendables that he is still fit to be their leader and do what they do best in order to save his son, and the younger team.
